{
  "texts": [
    "The search for transcriptional regulations in Bacillus subtilis returned 371 abstracts containing 2,865 sentences.",
    "The Sentence Eliminator-1 and Sentence Eliminator-2 rejected 1,184 and 692 sentences, respectively, leaving 989 sentences for RE.",
    "The process extracted 1,120 relations from these sentences.",
    "Through the refinement step in the GIX post-processing stage, the extracted relations were further processed and condensed into 706 interactions (shown in Fig 8).",
    "Ten-fold cross-validation results (%) P: Precision; R: Recall; F: F-score."
  ]
}